summary: This mod adds daedric masks to the game which can be crafted at the forge.
descriptionHtml:
I originally made this mod for myself to just have something else as a daedric helmet option. The Daedric Masks are almost identical to daedric helmet except they are not as heavy. There are two types of masks, one with the tusks and one without.

This mod allows crafting of daedric mask at the forge. They are standalone and do not replace anything.
author: lautasantenni
